---
import BaseLayout from "../layout/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.jsx";
import FooterReact from "../components/FooterReact.jsx";
---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="Privacy Policy"
  pageDescription="Read how YoutubersIncome.com handles your data, cookies, analytics, and privacy practices to keep your information safe and transparent."
  pageUrl="https://youtubersincome.com/privacy-policy"
>
  <Header />
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-6 text-gray-800">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
      At YoutubersIncome.com, your privacy is important to us. This policy
      outlines the types of data we collect and how we use it.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Data Collection</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
      We do not collect any personally identifiable information. When you use
      our site, we may log basic anonymous data such as:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2">
      <li>Browser type</li>
      <li>IP address (anonymized)</li>
      <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Cookies</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
      We may use cookies or third-party analytics tools (like Google Analytics)
      to understand how users interact with our site. This helps us improve our
      content and performance.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Usage</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
      All data we collect is used solely to improve the website. We do not sell,
      rent, or share your information with third parties.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. External Links</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
      Our site may contain links to other websites. We are not responsible for
      the privacy practices of those websites.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-lg">
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to email us
      at:
      <a href="mailto:nazrudeen.win@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 underline"
        >nazrudeen.win@gmail.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </section>
  <FooterReact />
</BaseLayout>
